quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,27,"Wama khalaqna assamaawal-arda wama baynahuma batilanthalika thannu allatheena kafaroofawaylun lillatheena kafaroo mina annar"
  38,28,"Am najAAalu allatheena amanoowaAAamiloo assalihati kalmufsideenafee al-ardi am najAAalu almuttaqeena kalfujjar"
  38,29,"Kitabun anzalnahu ilayka mubarakunliyaddabbaroo ayatihi waliyatathakkara olooal-albab"
  38,30,"Wawahabna lidawooda sulaymananiAAma alAAabdu innahu awwab"
  38,31,"Ith AAurida AAalayhi bilAAashiyyiassafinatu aljiyad"
  38,32,"Faqala innee ahbabtu hubbaalkhayri AAan thikri rabbee hatta tawaratbilhijab"
  38,33,"Ruddooha AAalayya fatafiqa mashanbissooqi wal-aAAnaq"
  38,34,"Walaqad fatanna sulaymanawaalqayna AAala kursiyyihi jasadan thumma anab"
  38,35,"Qala rabbi ighfir lee wahab leemulkan la yanbaghee li-ahadin min baAAdee innakaanta alwahhab"
  38,36,"Fasakhkharna lahu arreehatajree bi-amrihi rukhaan haythu asab"
  38,37,"Washshayateena kulla banna-inwaghawwas"
  38,38,"Waakhareena muqarraneena fee al-asfad"
  38,39,"Hatha AAataona famnunaw amsik bighayri hisab"
  38,40,"Wa-inna lahu AAindana lazulfawahusna maab"
  38,41,"Wathkur AAabdanaayyooba ith nada rabbahu annee massaniya ashshaytanubinusbin waAAathab"
  38,42,"Orkud birijlika hathamughtasalun baridun washarab"
